des:
How well do you know your Grand National runners, trainers, jockeys, race facts and general race knowledge?

Test your knowledge of the greatest steeplechase race in the world by playing the ultimate Grand National Quiz!

Each question has four multiple choice answers. Just say "a", "b", "c" or "d" to answer the question.

If you need a break, you can stop and come back at any time - the quiz will pick back up from the last question you answered.
